title: smapOne

creator: smapOne AG
descriptionHtml:
﻿With this app, you can use "smaps" created and shared with you using the smapOne platform. smaps are the smart way to digitize forms and processes easily and quickly. For a first look, you can try the demo smaps included in this app.

Features:

- Capture data anytime & anywhere
- Share tasks with your colleagues
- Generate and distribute detailed reports
- Use all smaps on- and offline

How does smapOne work? The smapOne app is part of the smapOne no-code platform. Digitize forms, questionnaires, checklists and other scenarios within 30 minutes using preconfigured modules. You can distribute your smaps to colleagues, teams or partners for use and then evaluate the data collected with them in the smapOne portal.
descriptionShort: ﻿Business processes natively available on an Android phone - in just 30 minutes!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: ﻿The new "Attach Document" module is available. This allows a PDF, Word, Excel or PowerPoint document to be selected from the mobile device in the form and attached to the submitted data record.
